Me voy a casar

00:37:49.590 --> 00:37:50.550
en una semana.

00:37:51.030 --> 00:37:52.030
Hoy solo envié

00:37:52.030 --> 00:37:52.880
solo envié decenas de copias.

00:37:53.800 --> 00:37:54.630
